    "Compare the use of powerset (minus empty set) frames as intuitionistic frames for Medvedev's [1966] \"logic of finite problems\" andSkvortsov's [1979] \"logic of infinite problems,\" as reviewed in, e.g., Definition 1 ofShatrov 2008.",
